"'''The Ballad of Master Vodo-Siosk Baas'''" was a ballad written by [[Tionne Solusar]] about the eponymous ancient [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]]. It recounted the betrayal and murder of [[Vodo-Siosk Baas]] by his former pupil, [[Exar Kun/Legends|Exar Kun]].

==Appearances==
*''[[Young Jedi Knights: Heirs of the Force]]''

